────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  CHANGELOG · 0.2.1                                                                                                     
  fix     rollout watch could miss the final ready event on slow clusters                                               
  fix     secret value zeroing on esc leaked one frame to the alt-screen buffer                                         
  fix     node-shell debug pod leaked when the exec session errored mid-attach                                          
  fix     helm history rollback picked the wrong revision after a fast-forward                                          
  new     resources editor accepts binary suffixes (Gi/Mi) case-insensitively                                           
  new     who-can query supports namespaced ClusterRoleBindings                                                         
  new     forwards registry survives a context switch mid-session                                                       
  perf    namespace palette CPU-share column no longer refetches per keystroke                                          
  perf    event dedupe groups now compute incrementally instead of full rescans                                         
  perf    YAML view syntax highlighting caches per-line instead of per-render                                           
  fix     PROD type-the-name modal accepted a trailing newline as a match                                               
  new     CRD printer columns now drive the generic list view's own sort keys                                           
                                                                                                                        
  ╭──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮  
